WEBVTT

00:10.487 --> 00:12.020
Gently.

00:12.105 --> 00:14.906
I can't do this.

00:14.941 --> 00:16.107
Yes, you can.

00:16.193 --> 00:18.409
Feel the layers.

00:23.116 --> 00:27.001
A man's flesh will
give to the blade.

00:34.261 --> 00:35.593
(inhales)

00:35.629 --> 00:38.463
Too much force.

00:38.515 --> 00:40.632
A gentler hand.

